# === SECURITY: never commit secrets ===
DeepSeek-api
*.env
.env*
**/secrets*
**/*api_key*
**/*apikey*
**/*.key

# raw benchflow job output logs the agent env (incl. DEEPSEEK_API_KEY) — never commit.
